t_wt <- xl %>%
   group_by(Transmitter, Genotype, ZT, Day) %>%
   dplyr::summarise(sum_wake = sum(Wake),
                    sum_sws = sum(SWS),
                    sum_ps = sum(PS),
                    sum_art = sum(Artifact))
## `summarise()` has grouped output by 'Transmitter', 'Genotype', 'ZT'. You can override using the `.groups` argument.
t_wt$PercentWake <- (t_wt$sum_wake / (t_wt$sum_sws + t_wt$sum_wake + t_wt$sum_ps + t_wt$sum_art))
t_wt$PercentSWS <- (t_wt$sum_sws / (t_wt$sum_sws + t_wt$sum_wake + t_wt$sum_ps + t_wt$sum_art))
t_wt$PercentPS <- (t_wt$sum_ps / (t_wt$sum_sws + t_wt$sum_wake + t_wt$sum_ps + t_wt$sum_art))
t_wt$PercentSleep <- ((t_wt$sum_sws + t_wt$sum_ps)/ (t_wt$sum_sws + t_wt$sum_wake + t_wt$sum_ps + t_wt$sum_art))

t_wt <- t_wt %>% dplyr::mutate(phase= ifelse(ZT>11, "dark", "light"))

t_wt$ZT <- as.factor(t_wt$ZT)

t_wt

## Degrees-of-freedom method: kenward-roger
#30 min bins (by TimeDay)
xl <- xl %>% dplyr::mutate(phase= ifelse(ZT>11, "dark", "light"))

t_wt_30 <- xl %>%
   group_by(Transmitter, Genotype, TimeDay, Day) %>%
   dplyr::summarise(phase=phase,
                    sum_wake = sum(Wake),
                    sum_sws = sum(SWS),
                    sum_ps = sum(PS),
                    sum_art = sum(Artifact))
## `summarise()` has grouped output by 'Transmitter', 'Genotype', 'TimeDay'. You can override using the `.groups` argument.
t_wt_30$PercentWake <- (t_wt_30$sum_wake / (t_wt_30$sum_sws + t_wt_30$sum_wake + t_wt_30$sum_ps + t_wt_30$sum_art))
t_wt_30$PercentSWS <- (t_wt_30$sum_sws / (t_wt_30$sum_sws + t_wt_30$sum_wake + t_wt_30$sum_ps + t_wt_30$sum_art))
t_wt_30$PercentPS <- (t_wt_30$sum_ps / (t_wt_30$sum_sws + t_wt_30$sum_wake + t_wt_30$sum_ps + t_wt_30$sum_art))
t_wt_30$PercentSleep <- ((t_wt_30$sum_sws + t_wt_30$sum_ps)/ (t_wt_30$sum_sws + t_wt_30$sum_wake + t_wt_30$sum_ps + t_wt_30$sum_art))

t_wt_30 <- t_wt_30 %>% mutate(TimeDay = str_remove_all(TimeDay, " "))

t_wt_30$TimeDay <- as.factor(t_wt_30$TimeDay)

                    mean_ps = mean(PercentPS),
                    mean_sleep = mean(PercentSleep))
